    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine is strong and reliable, showing no signs of leaks or mechanical distress, and the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. While there is some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all electronics are fully functional. This is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
